<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_5b37ead5-3c23-46d3-9c0a-ee06ca77ddc8" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="WA"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H9P3</sptc><title id="_6bf81513-3bd5-40d2-806d-1d0b567ecc78">Heated water use efficiency</title><archive-num>2019: WA 2.2(c)</archive-num><subclause id="_3a2f8cb7-79c9-4468-9e55-c0195886682a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d500fcfa-718d-4e7f-b61c-472b3a1ad66d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building must have features that, to the degree necessary, facilitate the efficient use of heated water appropriate to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_c090afa4-1499-4490-84fe-98a0020761e2">the geographic location of the building; and</li><li id="_0500fe37-f126-4073-9395-431afb2a132f">the available heated water supply for the building; and</li><li id="_7a3d83a3-f531-493d-8168-c928db8b6859">the function and use of the building.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_e61024b1-a8c9-469f-90bd-367d5f02ed53"><callout-type ncc-info-type="application"/><p>WA H9P3 only applies to Class 1 buildings, associated Class 10a buildings and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_6f584cb7-d446-4527-8ef5-4f0c60b880ff" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pools</xref> associated with a Class 1 building.</p></callout></clause>